<h4 class="card-title">Microsoft Technical aptitude syllabus</h4>
  <p class="card-text">•	C
<br>•	C++
<br>•	OOPS Concepts
<br>•	Basics of data structures
<br>•	Networking
<br>•	Windows ad
<br>•	Exchange servers
<br>•	DNS
<br>•	DHCP
